# PyCharm
#  JetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
#  be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
#  and can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
#  option (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
#.idea/

# Ignore everything under data/ by default, then whitelist demo asset dirs
# required by the inpaint-required Quickstart (canonical YAMLs + GT npz
# scaffolds + MSAs for the 5 bundled demo entries) + the existing data/demo/
# CIF + design_points inventory.
data/*
!data/demo/
!data/demo_canonical_yamls/
!data/demo_gt_structures/
!data/demo_msa/
scripts/phase0/
wandb/
playground/
.deepspeed_env
output/
outputs/
trainer_output/
checkpoints/
.vscode
*.pth

